name: ZDaemon's ULTIMATE CTF
description: A fresh change to Zdctfmp, we present you with Zdaemon's Ultimate CTF pack, which is Zdaemon's 2nd 'major' CTF pack to be released, but hopefully not 2nd best. This new 35 set level was created and compiled by some of Doom's best mappers, to bring you some of the best set of CTF maps ever.
